Variable          Purpose
path              To get and store the path of existing directory
url               To store the url of website for data download
activityLabels    To store the labels of different activities from the file
features          To store features list from the file
featuresWanted    Select only the required features with mean or std in their name
measurements      To store measurement values
train             To store X_train dataset
trainActivities   To store Y_train dataset
trainSubjects     To store subjects train dataset
test              To store X_test dataset
testActivities    To store Y_test dataset
testSubjects      To store subjects test dataset
combined          To store combined dataset
